{"tid":184411,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做平面設計係咪慘過狗？","createTime":"2017-04-02T18:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T05:46:56.000Z","uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"901bb77c246621f43afe4d2f4d8b3100de8b22fe","tid":184411,"uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:55:30.000Z","msg":"有少少想入行<br />\n係關於autocad果方面<br />\n係咪好辛苦？成日ot ?<br />\n畫autocad 呢啲工係咪要自己設計野？<br />\n出路如何？<br />\n有冇人可以講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45aefdef6bb335e754a96706d445d9b7d09e0bf6","tid":184411,"uid":24632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:57:52.000Z","msg":"做graphic 唔使用autocad ga wo...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：Freelance Graphic Designer，做freelance 好過做full time"},{"pid":"e14b74f749a6b2380141406c0ca961ffa5d1fac5","tid":184411,"uid":68389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做graphic 唔使用autocad ga wo...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：Freelance Graphic Designer，做freelance 好過做full time</blockquote><br />\n點搵freelance做？"},{"pid":"1e02af19e027375888133d883524b60f44721ae0","tid":184411,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有少少想入行<br />\n係關於autocad果方面<br />\n係咪好辛苦？成日ot ?<br />\n畫autocad 呢啲工係咪要自己設計野？<br />\n出路如何？<br />\n有冇人可以講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估巴打你可能有小小混淆左&quot;平面設計&quot;同出建築界/室內設計界的&quot;平面圖&quot;呢兩樣野<br />\n<br />\n通常我地講平面設計係指對網頁/廣告/印刷媒體/產品包裝...等類型的設計需求，autocad 畫出來嘅野都係&quot;平面&quot;, 但針對嘅係施工/工業上等對精準尺寸有要求的設計層面，多數以室內設計/建議為主<br />\n<br />\n至於&quot;畫autocad 呢啲工係咪要自己設計野？&quot;<br />\n這個問題沒有特定答案，睇你自己係走向designer / draftsman"},{"pid":"e703135672e0cc062b10f7c77d73782e45f181d6","tid":184411,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:42:21.000Z","msg":"回應返主題&quot;做平面設計係咪慘過狗&quot;<br />\n我個人認為，係香港不論各行各業，只要你係打緊工都係慘過隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過如果你加入嘅行業同時係你嘅興趣的話，會稍微降低呢種hard feeling"},{"pid":"61fa473a3165fb7974588c3cb98a774263042332","tid":184411,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T21:29:42.000Z","msg":"好似話做夠一年 咩捐贈器官卡都唔會派比你<br />\n咩肝呀腎呀 你死左拎來喂狗都冇狗食"},{"pid":"198b218cafd08323fbdfca65b9cc2d130d041ffa","tid":184411,"uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T01:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似話做夠一年 咩捐贈器官卡都唔會派比你<br />\n咩肝呀腎呀 你死左拎來喂狗都冇狗食</blockquote><br />\n即係唔洗訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508e6a14c2f64cb0ce254387e1329f02c880b2ac","tid":184411,"uid":93937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回應返主題&quot;做平面設計係咪慘過狗&quot;<br />\n我個人認為，係香港不論各行各業，只要你係打緊工都係慘過隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過如果你加入嘅行業同時係你嘅興趣的話，會稍微降低呢種hard feeling</blockquote><br />\n或者降低你既興趣得番hardfeeling<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa1fb773dace70a23e62a7aeaeb75620b629a6f","tid":184411,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>回應返主題&quot;做平面設計係咪慘過狗&quot;<br />\n我個人認為，係香港不論各行各業，只要你係打緊工都係慘過隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過如果你加入嘅行業同時係你嘅興趣的話，會稍微降低呢種hard feeling</blockquote><br />\n或者降低你既興趣得番hardfeeling<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"