normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打一份你有興趣既工只會令你遠離你既興趣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a638525b938e7e0432f126dc7aa25b73bc772015","tid":184411,"uid":97988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港做設計慘過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲人成日話IT狗IT狗，屌設計連狗都不如，樓主無啲咩遠大理想唔好入行，你會覺得做地盤仲開心"},{"pid":"16b5588260b79e7a19505cdf18103608823e024c","tid":184411,"uid":84484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係學生 係做freelancer Graphic Designer 大約八個鐘1000左右 我提議你學AI CorelDRAW PS 應該好夠 Autodesk 同 3DS就得閒學就夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD freelance通常透過咩途徑接？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前大學朋友介紹/以前公司客戶識開儲落<br />\n再唔係市面有好多freelance/ pt網<br />\n但通常做至少兩三年儲下人脈再岀黎freelance會smooth d<br />\n<br />\nBtw ft graphic 同freelance待遇同受既氣真係天同地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe69f1fe4cb8ef4566f23e2be4031e8bb920c87","tid":184411,"uid":84484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>回應返主題&quot;做平面設計係咪慘過狗&quot;<br />\n我個人認為，係香港不論各行各業，只要你係打緊工都係慘過隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過如果你加入嘅行業同時係你嘅興趣的話，會稍微降低呢種hard feeling</blockquote><br />\n或者降低你既興趣得番hardfeeling<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打一份你有興趣既工只會令你遠離你既興趣</blockquote><br />\n世界大戰既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人經驗係雖然會令你興趣減少少<br />\n但睇下成日岀黎會有滿足感既<br />\n<br />\n利申 做dm/poster/branding graphic"},{"pid":"116bc9adf69d2e87450cb40acb3a1f55d842aba4","tid":184411,"uid":84484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>回應返主題&quot;做平面設計係咪慘過狗&quot;<br />\n我個人認為，係香港不論各行各業，只要你係打緊工都係慘過隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過如果你加入嘅行業同時係你嘅興趣的話，會稍微降低呢種hard feeling</blockquote><br />\n或者降低你既興趣得番hardfeeling<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打一份你有興趣既工只會令你遠離你既興趣</blockquote><br />\n世界大戰既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人經驗係雖然會令你興趣減少少<br />\n但睇下成<span style=\"color: red;\">品</span>岀黎會有滿足感既<br />\n<br />\n利申 做dm/poster/branding graphic</blockquote>"},{"pid":"99893f3821db7c410bd10890cc8ad92a57ff4cd5","tid":184411,"uid":96128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"設計黎講freelance好做好多"},{"pid":"f7bd375ddca5ae4129f7cfec22801a2551ccd1be","tid":184411,"uid":68389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>設計黎講freelance好做好多</blockquote><br />\n但係會唔穩定...<br />\n會唔會搵少好多？"},{"pid":"d6eca78a89dca2d8a37296f12b66421ce73f3556","tid":184411,"uid":96128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>設計黎講freelance好做好多</blockquote><br />\n但係會唔穩定...<br />\n會唔會搵少好多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會架 但係唔洗好似fulltime咁日日坐係度 又要對上司咁<br />\n就真係做到隻狗咁<br />\nFreelance又可以自己報價 時間又彈性好多 得閒既可以搵份長工/pt 再接freelance"},{"pid":"df55608e6ed13d31c0f22cd0109589cbcfcbd27b","tid":184411,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"做design最on9就係,你上司唔識design野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其次就係D工作狂designer升上去既老屎忽,乜鳩都叫你試一餐<br />\n明明未試已經知到會有咩結果,係都要你晒時間試一次俾佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm